response.overview: On December 05, 2017, Oita Event Hall in Oita hosted Day 14 of NJPW World Tag League 2017.  The main event featured Los Ingobernables de Japon (EVIL, SANADA & Tetsuya Naito) vs CHAOS (Gedo, Hirooki Goto & Kazuchika Okada).  The card also featured Best Friends (Beretta & Chuckie T) vs CHAOS (Tomohiro Ishii & Toru Yano).  Other wrestlers on the show include Davey Boy Smith Jr., Lance Archer, and Minoru Suzuki, and more!
response.title: NJPW World Tag League 2017: Day 14
